name: Voxelglyph
description: The Voxelglyph represents membership to Fingerprints DAO and is the result of a direct partnership between Larva Labs and Fingerprints, granting access to all member perks and exposure to its renowned collection. It consists of a script in Java stored entirely on-chain that, when executed, will take Autoglyph #134's characters as input and generate coordinates for the 3D artwork. More information about Fingerprints DAO is available at https://fingerprintsdao.xyz.
